    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> 5th level</em></p>\n<p>You add additional chemicals to your modified biochemist's pack. When you restore hit points with a tech power or class feature, you can use your Biochemist's Touch and Potent Mixture features.</p>\n<p>Additionally, when you use your Invigorating Mixture to grant temporary hit points to a creature, you can choose to restore that many hit points to the same creature. You can use this feature three times. You gain an additional use at 9th, 13th, and 17th level. You regain all expended uses when you complete a short or long rest.</p>",
